{
  "id": "vRFcG5n6",
  "slug": "tooltip-overhaul",
  "title": "Tooltip Overhaul",
  "description": "Every tooltip, clearer and cleaner",
  "body": "<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Tooltip Overhaul ✨</strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A complete visual refresh for Minecraft tooltips, completely replacing the vanilla tooltip system with a clearer layout. Every tooltip, <em>more modern, sharper, clearer</em>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Core Features</strong> 🔧</h1>\n<p>📜 <strong>Scrollable Tooltips</strong> - When a tooltip is too tall and goes beyond the screen limits, you can <em>scroll</em> through its content.<br>✂️ <strong>Text Wrapping</strong> - Prevents tooltips from being too wide by <em>inserting line breaks</em> where needed.<br>🦋​ <strong>Equipment Comparison</strong> - Built in toggleable equipment comparison functionality for comparison of armor pieces with the currently equipped one. You can change the keybind in-game.<br>🤝 <strong>Compatibility</strong> - Works with <em>JEI</em>, <em>EMI</em>, <em>ModernFix</em>, <em>Flerovium</em>, <em>FTB Quests</em>, <em>Apotheosis</em>, <em>etc</em>.<br>🎨 <strong>Maximum Customization</strong> - You can change, crop, expand and move <em>whatever</em> you want! <em>Customize</em> freely among a big variety of options!<br>📊 <strong>Rating Element</strong> - Just below the item name, a <em>rarity/qualifier</em> appears (configurable, off by default).<br>⚡ <strong>Effects &amp; Frames</strong> - Choose from animated <em>frames</em>, overlays, and custom styles, among other content.<br>🧩 <strong>Mod Compatibility</strong> - Any mod can add its own custom frames.<br>🌀 <strong>3D Item Rendering</strong> - A 3D icon appears when hovering over items.<br>🎲 <strong>Vignette</strong> - A new type of decoration that allows you to add internal gradients of various shapes to the tooltip.<br>❄️ <strong>In-game config screen</strong> - Additionally, a fully custom config screen can be opened to access the settings from within the game.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: verdana;\">📦 <em><strong>By default, some vanilla items include frames.</strong></em><br>If you like the idea, we can create custom frames for the most requested mods and add native support. 🙌</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: verdana;\">This mod is highly configurable. For any questions, problems, contributions, new ideas about content/mods, and more, you can join our <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/linkout?remoteUrl=https://discord.com/invite/Pxj3gdhGj8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">💬 official Discord</a> and comment in the appropriate channels.</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/Pxj3gdhGj8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1018043/description_a255b953-62ec-43d7-b4b3-8a1a94b36bac.png\" alt=\"Discord Banner\"></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: verdana;\">All bug reports or feature request should be directed to me, you can join our <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/Pxj3gdhGj8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">Discord server</a>.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong>Configuration ⚙️</strong></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">There are <strong>two </strong>ways to configure the tooltips: <em>globally </em>or <em>specifically</em>. 📝</span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;For <strong>global configurations</strong>, you must modify the file </span></span> <code>config/tooltipoverhaul/tooltipoverhaul.toml</code><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, which contains configuration options that apply equally to all items.</span></span></li>\n<li>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;For <strong>specific configurations</strong> <em>(for particular items, tags or namespaces/modids)</em>, you must modify the file located at&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;<code>config/tooltipoverhaul/custom_frames.json</code><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">. For more information on how to work with this file, please follow this <a href=\"https://github.com/Xylonity/Tooltip-Overhaul/wiki/Configuration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>wiki</strong></a>.</span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>To reload the <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">specific configurations</span>, you can use the command <code>'/tooltipoverhaul reload'</code> without having to restart the game, while global settings are reloaded automatically!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong>Resource Packs 🎨</strong></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Resource Packs</strong> can also be created in order to add custom frames or custom configurations. For more information, check the <a href=\"https://github.com/Xylonity/Tooltip-Overhaul/wiki/Custom-Frame\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>wiki</strong></a>.<br></span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Check out</strong> the following <em>texture packs</em>, which add <em>more</em> frames and features!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/jolly-tooltips\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_139f83d7-2461-4ef3-a360-c3eeb241a7cb.gif\" alt=\"\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong>Showcase 📷</strong></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For extra information, check the <a href=\"https://github.com/Xylonity/Tooltip-Overhaul/wiki/Content-and-examples\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">wiki</a>.</span></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Icon animations</strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>zoom</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_710de09a-00ff-4dbf-a52c-e7fd191a8238.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>rotate</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_96fcdc92-aec7-4e72-8362-0afc6bf10907.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>rotate_fast</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_f662105e-aaac-45f1-9fcd-86e07fc98f25.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>rotate_zoom</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_8e693f98-e831-4747-a49a-780caaac7e4f.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>zoom_snap</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_0801c7e9-7401-4411-9813-55470e190b0f.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>skew</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_daf92bbe-e6e4-4615-bd68-9c9e7445f77e.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>vibration</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_da3a6e73-2f1f-4351-8708-1eeac1fb7c2c.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>tilt_wave</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_e9de8114-60b6-4eea-9490-165cd845469f.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>flip</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_7ade282e-49b3-4c28-bdb2-d7a77d610bf3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>pendulum</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_e907728e-75aa-4f50-8115-d457a7eeeb19.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>bounce</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_867a38c4-1f48-4396-a8bf-9504fab84ea3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>go_down</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_b39aef12-e088-4801-8971-7962fbef5c99.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>pulse</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_d41863b1-11a5-4c07-a127-ff15524f20ab.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>fan_in</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_5c43e9d5-03fc-4497-8c1b-c2c367c32a9c.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>hover_pop</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_da470af0-1239-4df2-ad7f-64c6bd63405f.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>barrel_roll</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_e8ea3b98-47b1-42a9-bdb0-e26d2c7eb643.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Effects</strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>metal_shining</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qFedqV8.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p><br>nebula<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_745e0555-e12a-43df-abfb-0f4b48e7af3a.gif\" width=\"398\" height=\"224\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>echo</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_c9a01ea9-6960-479a-8bb2-cce21d559607.gif\" width=\"401\" height=\"226\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>speed_lines</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_14d36d67-1da3-4bcd-a606-196a7286913a.gif\" width=\"405\" height=\"228\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>white_dust</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_85b3c1da-5800-4828-a267-092facdfad7c.gif\" width=\"403\" height=\"227\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>galaxy</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_55e6c529-e55d-440a-a78b-9996fcc93731.gif\" width=\"401\" height=\"226\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>spiral</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_0607039c-7936-4500-8753-89dde6b156df.gif\" width=\"401\" height=\"226\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>orbs</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_1d08b434-77a6-4808-b0c8-32f06abe3ee7.gif\" width=\"401\" height=\"226\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>rim_light</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o0gMIwU.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>ripples</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FwumAw7.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>sonar</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LRU7jVR.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>stars</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wiTPtpy.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>cinder</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/N1Yfe7n.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"180\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Frame overlays</strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>- amber_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_baca4ef8-e32c-4943-9b72-585d14a90757.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- amethyst_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_9422751d-3e2e-4924-a7b0-8b49d1eb11f2.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- angelical_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_6dcb7eeb-a5dd-4ac0-9480-cb60ee7a7ad4.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- battle_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_07bf3456-f9c7-4345-8faf-9889396b8228.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- cataclysm_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_ebb1c767-10e9-48e2-8567-456b1b84f968.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- demonic_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_ca5a36e8-c693-4b07-a6a6-67c2fa92c023.gif\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- diamond_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_ab4b1236-659a-4298-9cae-5ef103383adb.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- emerald_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_5abf01b7-b648-4d8e-b6bc-cec029a5c625.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- fire_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_98c0ee0f-c1ea-4620-9b42-c6e56b3c517a.gif\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- flower_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_6fa506ba-30e1-4be4-ac7a-0b18dce1c40c.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- frost_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_82bb29a5-bf61-4186-bcdd-ca90c1d0bd65.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- futuristic_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_154869a1-340b-4deb-b9e8-a00caadf06ec.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- gear_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_16478723-c99c-43ff-aef9-68ab9a090a2d.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- guns_and_wires.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_6dd81020-a327-41e8-b640-9d6f8ac33b29.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- king_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_71c9dfbc-f1f0-48d5-a11d-dde888bdb800.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- silver_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_4081bd7d-3705-471c-b5ab-5ebe9c7749e8.png\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- steampunk_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_b1791fca-e20c-4183-a611-7a15c8e1a416.gif\" width=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- zombie_brain_frame.png</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_e322c1ae-aa48-40d8-a2e4-8c3ea88e7c32.png\" width=\"264\"><br>- draconic_fire_frame.png</p>\n<p><br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_813f2120-06a1-44aa-97d3-05e85879f9d5.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- medieval_crossroads_frame.png&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_5dfb890e-cf0f-4f6b-8347-746d71621fff.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- plasma_lamp_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_e8e0178f-f2d5-435c-be18-e627cb71359e.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- neon_fire_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_43e24e70-d5ae-4949-aa4a-c3e5d38658c4.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- garden_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_3334b176-b44e-44b1-aba3-7f339b50fd71.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- construction_punk_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_2a25eb06-6e05-42fc-92fd-08ccd3c6f31e.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- cavemen_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_eb0d181c-18b6-41b6-820a-eba6a274ac56.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- nuclear_alarm_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_e3ccf7cc-938a-49f2-ab90-1033399627a2.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- gummy_bear_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_2e288886-4f4c-4f88-9e3a-517473b8d07f.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- greek_temple_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_a37f58df-8ba9-4ce0-b63a-12c938fb34d9.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p><br>- pure_alchemy_frame.png</p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_ea50cd7b-0819-4fb4-a8f6-057989d94d91.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n<p>- skyland_frame.png<br><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_25f8541e-a6d9-4a3e-a069-79ebccc0ee17.png\" width=\"264\" height=\"264\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Vignettes</strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>circular</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_0cba7784-f252-4ec4-9205-efb9963933a0.gif\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>hole</p>\n<p><img><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_58beecac-0e05-43e8-aa29-4e367af662db.gif\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<h2><strong>Maximum customization</strong></h2>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p>Different styles!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NsOvwXU.gif\" width=\"600\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Chain effects together!</p>\n<p><img><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1327508/description_c16824dd-21a7-4d09-8f3d-9761b1f194d6.gif\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong>Aditional info 📝</strong></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod is completely client-sided.</span></span></p>\n<p><em><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Neither Fabric nor Forge versions require external dependencies, so just download this mod, drop it inside your mods folder and start playing!</span></span></em></p>\n<p><em>To access the in-game configuration in the Fabric version, you will need&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/modmenu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">ModMenu</a>!</em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><strong>Credits 📦</strong></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Xylonity - Programmer and mod designer</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">TheModderG - Tooltip overlays and mod icon designer</span></span></p>",
